you thought he said zit...

03:23.803 --> 03:25.430
and you asked for seconds.

03:25.538 --> 03:28.735
-Now, out the window!
-We're not going anywhere.

03:28.841 --> 03:32.299
-We came for a pillow fight.
-Connie's dad took them all.

03:33.246 --> 03:35.510
Then how about just fight?

03:35.615 --> 03:36.639
[groaning]

03:36.749 --> 03:37.807
What was that? What....

03:37.917 --> 03:38.884
[Kahn screaming]

03:38.985 --> 03:41.249
No boys in slumber party!

03:41.788 --> 03:43.756
Oh, hey, Chang.

03:44.057 --> 03:47.049
How you doing? How's your dad?

03:47.260 --> 03:50.058
Still on membership committee
at Nine River Country Club?

03:50.163 --> 03:51.858
Yes, sir, Mr. Soup.

03:51.965 --> 03:55.457
We were just walking by and we saw
Bobby sneaking in the window...

03:55.568 --> 03:58.298
and I wanted to make sure
Connie was okay.

03:58.404 --> 04:00.201
Bobby Hill, out the window!

04:01.674 --> 04:04.939
Chang, you and your friends
may use the door.

04:05.211 --> 04:06.405
[crickets chirping]

04:08.681 --> 04:09.705
[groaning]

04:09.816 --> 04:12.683
All right, guys. The girls aren't here.

04:12.785 --> 04:15.310
